Product description

The Vivo Y100 5G features colour-changing fluorite AG glass that changes colour with changes in environment and time. The 64 MP OIS anti-shake camera helps to take steady and cinematic images without any hassle. This smartphone has 8 GB RAM with an additional 8 GB of extended RAM, which allows you to keep up to 27 apps in the background. It uses a powerful MediaTek Dimensity 900 processor to give you a smooth 5G experience, and its 4500 mAh battery with 44 W FlashCharge lets the phones battery last for a long time This smartphone has many camera features, so you can create vlogs, movies, and click portraits as you desire. The Funtouch OS 13, allows you to have a secure OS experience, in addition to that you can also enjoy personalised settings, privacy protection, and much more.
